pkgnet-report.Rmd

This report on MiscMetabar is generated by pkgnet, an R package for analyzing other R packages through the lens of network theory.

Dependency Network

This section analyzes the recursive package dependencies of MiscMetabar.

In the plot below, you’ll see the following colors:

  • orange: MiscMetabar
  • gray: R packages available in every R session by default
  • green: third-party R packages
